PrecisAppointment of Catherine Ebbs-Lepage, of Swift Current, Saskatchewan, as a full-time member of the National Parole Board to hold office during good behaviour for a term of ten years; designation of the said Catherine Ebbs-Lepage as a full-time member of the Appeal Division of the National Parole Board; and designation of Catherine Ebbs-Lepage as Vice-Chairperson of the Appeal Division of the National Parole Board.
